keeping her safe.

07:13.207 --> 07:15.735
Hey Meg, it's time
to answer me, please.

07:55.574 --> 07:56.566
- Meg!
- Meg!

07:59.350 --> 08:00.118
Meg, Meg.

08:00.151 --> 08:01.014
Meg, talk to me, Meg.

