something here, Meg, please.

08:06.455 --> 08:07.126
Help her, help!

08:07.159 --> 08:08.471
Did you eat something?

08:08.502 --> 08:09.878
Come on, give me
something here, Meg.

08:09.910 --> 08:11.415
- Meg, please, Meg.
- Meg!

08:11.447 --> 08:14.102
- What is it? What happened?
- Jack, do something!

