12:35.286 --> 12:36.375
- of this situation.
- Hey, I know.

12:40.374 --> 12:41.206
Mommy.

12:43.607 --> 12:44.982
I mean, come...

12:49.654 --> 12:51.542
Want to just go home?

12:53.558 --> 12:54.390
Yeah?

12:57.047 --> 12:59.510
Yeah, okay.

12:59.542 --> 13:01.270
Okay, babycakes.

13:01.302 --> 13:02.678
Time for bed.

13:03.350 --> 13:05.270
I told you, off your tablet.

13:05.302 --> 13:06.102
Let's go.

