but I saw you.

13:15.319 --> 13:16.630
Stop it.

13:18.902 --> 13:20.791
Meg, let go, please.

13:24.502 --> 13:25.302
Thank you.

13:35.254 --> 13:38.327
Did I ever tell you about
the day I met your mommy?

13:42.774 --> 13:47.318
She was about your age and
you look exactly like her.

13:48.662 --> 13:51.703
Well, she was here
visiting her Uncle Eli

13:51.735 --> 13:56.567
and I was in the backyard
pruning my rosebush,

13:57.846 --> 14:00.343
and she would stop
and pretend like

14:00.375 --> 14:02.038
she was looking somewhere else

14:02.071 --> 14:04.215
when I tried to get her eye.

14:05.111 --> 14:08.119
But I knew she wanted to
know what I was doing.

14:08.151 --> 14:12.598
So I finally did catch her
eye and I smiled at her.

14:13.591 --> 14:17.591
And I think that made her
brave enough to come over.

14:18.679 --> 14:21.174
And when she walked up to me,

14:21.942 --> 14:23.926
I handed her a rose.

14:26.678 --> 14:30.486
It was such a beautiful
pale pink rose.

14:31.414 --> 14:35.927
And she looked up at me
with the sweetest smile.

14:38.743 --> 14:42.902
And we've been fast
friends ever since.

14:44.918 --> 14:49.750
