I are fast friends now,

14:50.838 --> 14:53.047
just like me and your mommy.

15:00.823 --> 15:01.719
No, huh?

15:04.054 --> 15:04.695
Okay.

15:08.535 --> 15:10.902
You want me to sing
you a song before I go?

15:12.694 --> 15:13.335
Just go.

15:18.806 --> 15:20.087
Okay.

15:20.119 --> 15:23.222
Night night, don't
let the bed bugs bite.

15:31.062 --> 15:34.359
So I went back and checked
on her just a little while ago

15:34.391 --> 15:38.199
and had to take her tablet
away from her again.

15:38.231 --> 15:40.726
But the
poor little thing,

15:40.758 --> 15:42.039
she's so exhausted.

15:42.071 --> 15:44.342
She's gonna be asleep soon.

15:44.374 --> 15:45.526
You think I should

15:45.558 --> 15:46.294
- check on her or...
- It sounds like

15:46.326 --> 15:47.703
she's calming down.

15:47.735 --> 15:49.687
She needs to get used to
falling asleep without you.

15:49.719 --> 15:52.982
I could tell that
she was a little sad,

15:53.014 --> 15:54.615
so I tried to distract her

15:54.647 --> 15:55.607
and it worked for a little bit.

15:55.639 --> 15:58.359
We danced for awhile.

15:58.391 --> 16:00.854
But then she said that
she had a stomachache

16:00.886 --> 16:03.255
and wanted to be
alone in her room.

16:03.287 --> 16:07.478
I realized I should've taken
the tablet away sooner.

16:07.510 --> 16:08.983
Sorry about that.

16:09.015 --> 16:10.743
That's my fault, I
shouldn't have told her

16:10.775 --> 16:11.863
she could use it.

16:11.895 --> 16:15.126
That's, I don't know, it's
all a little bit new for us.

16:15.158 --> 16:16.663
Hmm.

16:16.695 --> 16:19.575
Hey, we couldn't
do this without you.

16:19.607 --> 16:22.455
You help keep this
family sane.

16:22.487 --> 16:23.894
Oh no, no, no.

16:23.926 --> 16:24.982
- Oh, come on.
- This is on me.

16:25.014 --> 16:26.167
- Nope, it's on me.
- Come on.

16:26.199 --> 16:28.886
I'm happy you guys had
a night out together.

16:28.918 --> 16:30.103
- Thank you, goodnight.
- Thank you, Marissa.

16:30.135 --> 16:31.478
- We really appreciate you.
- You bet.

16:34.935 --> 16:37.238
Sounds
like she's asleep.

16:37.270 --> 16:38.743
It's the little steps, right?

16:40.246 --> 16:42.966
Yeah.

17:13.717 --> 17:16.214
Meg.

18:07.606 --> 18:08.437
Oh, Jesus.

18:09.911 --> 18:11.671
Meg, sweetie.

18:11.703 --> 18:14.487
Hey, you need to go to bed.

18:36.534 --> 18:37.366
Hey.

18:44.566 --> 18:46.071
Hey, are you okay, sweetie?

18:48.247 --> 18:49.079
Meg.

18:51.831 --> 18:53.430
Hey, Meggie, Meg.

18:57.111 --> 19:00.567
Hey, did you have
a bad dream, hmm?

19:00.599 --> 19:01.527
Okay, come on.

19:01.559 --> 19:03.414
It's okay, lay down.

19:03.447 --> 19:04.950
Okay, all right.

19:08.566 --> 19:11.766
Here you go.

19:11.797 --> 19:13.111
Close your eyes.

20:29.847 --> 20:30.678
Mommy.

20:49.654 --> 20:52.246
Jack.

20:55.927 --> 20:58.326
Crap.

21:06.934 --> 21:08.311
- Mommy?
- Ssh, hi.

21:09.430 --> 21:11.159
You don't have to
get up yet, okay?

21:11.191 --> 21:12.023
Don't leave.

21:13.174 --> 21:14.134
I love you.

21:14.167 --> 21:15.702
I'll be right back, okay?

21:15.735 --> 21:18.421
- I love you.
