21:30.135 --> 21:31.127
Jack, she...

21:31.991 --> 21:33.526
She called out, okay?

21:33.559 --> 21:37.270
And then I think she
was sleepwalking or,

21:38.903 --> 21:41.430
I don't know, at least I
think she was sleepwalking.

21:44.727 --> 21:47.767
You seemed okay with me
checking on her before.

21:47.799 --> 21:48.919
Checking on her, I get.

21:48.950 --> 21:50.327
I understand, I just,

21:51.799 --> 21:54.550
when you spend all night
with her, it's just,

21:56.470 --> 21:58.486
I just really miss
having you next to me.

22:00.694 --> 22:01.303
Oh.

22:02.646 --> 22:03.255
Listen.

22:04.791 --> 22:05.847
Just give me a call after
your meeting with Ashe.

22:05.878 --> 22:07.126
And I'll see you later.

22:07.159 --> 22:08.471
Okay, hold on.

22:09.783 --> 22:11.895
Okay, I gave in, I'm sorry.

22:12.919 --> 22:14.743
Okay, I'm sorry too.

22:16.086 --> 22:17.175
Last night I was,

22:18.358 --> 22:19.127
I was a real asshole.

22:19.158 --> 22:21.303
Mm, mm-hmm.

22:22.263 --> 22:23.094
Comes naturally.

22:24.406 --> 22:25.911
Wow.

22:25.943 --> 22:28.054
That's cute.

22:28.087 --> 22:29.943
All right, I'll see you later.

22:29.974 --> 22:32.374
Mm, Jack, here.

22:32.406 --> 22:33.974
Hey, I am trying.

22:34.006 --> 22:35.511
I know you are.

22:35.543 --> 22:36.438
We're both trying.

22:37.558 --> 22:38.614
I'll see you tonight.

