to go to class.

23:00.919 --> 23:01.719
Meg.

23:04.182 --> 23:06.038
Why don't you want to
be at school today?

23:10.294 --> 23:12.630
Please, just one day?

23:15.031 --> 23:15.831
Meg.

23:16.791 --> 23:17.974
You need to answer me.

23:19.094 --> 23:21.046
I can't help you if
you don't answer me.

23:23.318 --> 23:24.631
Why do you want to go home?

23:27.318 --> 23:28.247
Because.

23:30.358 --> 23:31.479
My tummy hurts.

23:33.430 --> 23:34.806
And sometimes my throat.

23:34.838 --> 23:37.878
Yep, yep, and this is
what is getting worse.

23:41.239 --> 23:43.126
I'm sorry to hear that, Meg.

23:43.159 --> 23:45.847
