24:23.031 --> 24:25.974
Meg, do you miss your mom a lot

24:26.007 --> 24:27.223
when you're not with her?

24:28.535 --> 24:29.174
Yes.

24:30.647 --> 24:32.086
Does your
stomach and throat hurt

24:32.119 --> 24:33.398
only when you miss her?

24:34.903 --> 24:35.926
Yes.

24:39.382 --> 24:42.071
That's a mean
old monster, huh?

24:46.423 --> 24:48.247
I want to thank
you for coming in.

24:48.278 --> 24:51.798
I know it's probably uncomfortable
being here right now.

24:51.831 --> 24:53.974
But since you're here,
is there anything extra...

24:54.007 --> 24:54.903
Is Meg okay?

24:55.767 --> 24:56.950
I mean,

24:56.983 --> 25:00.246
I mean, she's so
attached to me now

25:00.278 --> 25:03.255
and she's still so attached
to her bear, Ricky,

25:03.286 --> 25:05.975
and I don't know,
last night I found her

25:06.006 --> 25:08.470
sitting up in bed and she
was staring at nothing

25:08.503 --> 25:09.782
and I just thought...

25:13.974 --> 25:16.023
What? You thought what?

25:17.206 --> 25:18.038
Nothing.

25:21.110 --> 25:23.511
I don't know, it's
just hard for me.

25:24.471 --> 25:27.062
She's so much like I was.

25:27.095 --> 25:29.302
Or I don't know,
like I am now and...

25:32.055 --> 25:33.238
But she wasn't at first, right?

25:33.271 --> 25:35.158
She was fearless and
I just thought that

25:35.191 --> 25:37.751
she wouldn't be like me and...

25:40.951 --> 25:42.807
I don't know, even
through, all the...

25:45.591 --> 25:46.422
Yeah.

25:47.863 --> 25:51.318
She was never attached
like this to me or to Jack

25:51.351 --> 25:54.038
and definitely not to
some stuffed animal, so.

25:55.191 --> 25:59.446
Well, there's really nothing
unusual about her behavior.

25:59.479 --> 26:03.254
