that's suffering from anxiety.

26:03.286 --> 26:07.415
And the bear, Ricky,
is her comfort object.

26:07.446 --> 26:09.366
He helps her feel safe.

26:09.398 --> 26:12.406
And after he seizure
at the park, you know,

26:12.438 --> 26:13.591
her attachment to you,

26:13.622 --> 26:15.670
her mother and her caregiver,

26:15.703 --> 26:17.110
it makes more sense.

26:17.142 --> 26:18.614
It really scared her.

26:23.446 --> 26:27.127
